data.description:
Welcome to the pinnacle of urban living at 1801 S Dunkirk Street Unit #303, Aurora, Colorado 80017. This exceptional condo offers a perfect blend of contemporary design, comfort, and convenience, creating an inviting space to call home.

As you enter this well-appointed unit, you are greeted by an open and airy floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The living room exudes warmth and charm with its gas fireplace, also featuring large windows that flood the space with natural light and provide scenic views. Step out onto your private balcony, a perfect retreat to enjoy your morning coffee or unwind after a long day.

The stylish kitchen is a chef's delight, showcasing modern appliances, and ample cabinet space for all your culinary needs. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or enjoying a quiet meal, this kitchen is both functional and aesthetically pleasing.

This unit boasts two bedrooms, each providing a comfortable and tranquil escape. The primary suite features a spacious bedroom, a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom, offering a luxurious sanctuary. The second bedroom is versatile, perfect for family, guests or a home office.

Convenience is key with in-unit laundry facilities, 1 car garage with an additional reserved parking space. The community amenities are equally impressive, including a community pool, playground and meticulously maintained grounds.

Located in the vibrant city of Aurora, this condo is centrally positioned for easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and major transportation routes. Enjoy the nearby parks and recreational areas, adding to the overall appeal of this prime location.

Don't miss the opportunity to make 1801 S Dunkirk Street Unit #303 your new address. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of modern living in Aurora, Colorado! This condo is a true gem waiting for the perfect owner to call it home.

Pictures have been virtually staged
